WEBVTT

01:32.080 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:37.970
[Episode 14]

01:52.450 --> 01:56.220
[A few hours ago]

01:53.710 --> 01:54.970
You have good taste.

01:57.229 --> 01:58.000
Excuse me, please.

01:58.000 --> 01:59.229
Have a look!

02:54.840 --> 02:56.240
Running into the two of us

02:56.560 --> 02:57.960
means you're out of luck.

03:02.990 --> 03:03.650
Master Bei,

03:04.030 --> 03:05.150
this mechanism of yours

03:05.150 --> 03:06.810
is really cleverly designed.

03:08.000 --> 03:09.130
Stab me with it again

03:09.700 --> 03:12.360
and I'll make it malfunction.
Do you believe me?

03:12.840 --> 03:13.770
I-I believe you.

03:13.840 --> 03:14.640
I believe you.

03:21.030 --> 03:21.570
Mr. Bei,

03:22.310 --> 03:24.680
I think you should keep dressing
as a woman.

03:24.680 --> 03:26.000
Your own face...

03:26.400 --> 03:27.200
What about it?

03:28.280 --> 03:28.960
It's ugly.

03:33.050 --> 03:35.240
So I get beaten for telling the truth?

03:46.560 --> 03:47.150
Useless!

03:46.660 --> 03:55.070
[Shou'an Palace]

03:48.430 --> 03:49.870
All of you are useless!

03:56.030 --> 03:58.400
The Empress Dowager summoned
many strategists overnight.

03:58.400 --> 03:59.560
Judging by this scene,

03:59.560 --> 04:00.690
she must be furious.

04:02.840 --> 04:04.360
We fought well in this battle.

04:04.360 --> 04:05.520
Using Prince Duan's hand,

04:05.520 --> 04:08.030
we eliminated the experts
around the Empress Dowager

04:08.030 --> 04:10.840
and dispelled Prince Duan's suspicions
about Mr. Bei.

04:10.840 --> 04:12.240
Two birds with one stone.

04:13.840 --> 04:14.700
Not bad indeed,

04:14.960 --> 04:16.290
but let's not get cocky.

04:16.630 --> 04:19.230
When the fight between them
is nearing its end,

04:19.240 --> 04:21.070
there won't be much time for you
to lie low

04:21.070 --> 04:22.280
and bide your time.

04:28.480 --> 04:29.210
What is this?

04:29.750 --> 04:30.750
Bai gave it to you.

04:33.190 --> 04:34.060
Let me explain.

04:34.190 --> 04:35.250
No need to explain.

04:35.560 --> 04:37.000
It's rare for him to be so thoughtful.

04:37.000 --> 04:37.730
Just keep it.

04:40.870 --> 04:41.470
That's...

04:42.240 --> 04:42.950
That's it?

04:44.070 --> 04:45.270
What else should I do?

04:46.950 --> 04:48.880
Stop pretending to be so generous.

04:49.310 --> 04:50.600
Aren't you usually quite jealous?

04:50.600 --> 04:51.830
So what if you're the emperor?

04:51.830 --> 04:53.270
Can you guarantee she won't be bullied?

04:53.270 --> 04:54.000
That I can do.

04:54.120 --> 04:54.750
Then can you guarantee

04:54.750 --> 04:56.360
that among all the women in the world,
she'll be the only one you want?

04:56.360 --> 04:57.090
That's easy.

05:02.390 --> 05:03.000
You...

05:03.680 --> 05:06.210
don't have anything else
you want to say to me?

05:06.920 --> 05:08.180
What else should I say?

05:09.240 --> 05:09.900
You tell me.

05:13.160 --> 05:14.290
The Empress Dowager

05:14.800 --> 05:16.750
will definitely find every excuse

05:18.120 --> 05:20.450
to make things difficult for Prince Duan.

05:23.070 --> 05:23.800
So let's...

05:24.270 --> 05:25.070
Let's do what?

05:27.680 --> 05:28.510
Let's...

05:35.040 --> 05:35.720
No rush.

05:37.580 --> 05:39.840
Let's wait until everything's settled.

05:43.320 --> 05:44.930
I really can't understand.

05:45.040 --> 05:47.040
Why did Concubine Yu do such a thing?

05:47.070 --> 05:49.120
She's already
the most favored in the harem.

05:49.120 --> 05:51.320
Why did she do something so despicable?

05:51.600 --> 05:52.350
That servant

05:52.510 --> 05:54.370
kept insisting it was his own idea

05:54.430 --> 05:56.230
and had nothing to do with her.

05:56.830 --> 05:59.040
Concubine Yu really managed
to wash her hands of it completely.

05:59.040 --> 06:00.170
Wash her hands of it?

06:00.390 --> 06:02.650
Then why did she end up
in the Cold Palace?

06:02.680 --> 06:03.540
Let me tell you,

06:03.720 --> 06:05.560
she's miserable in the Cold Palace.

06:05.560 --> 06:06.390
Nonsense.

06:06.390 --> 06:07.560
Who's talking nonsense?

06:07.560 --> 06:09.160
Go to the Cold Palace
and see for yourself.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.000
How dare you!

06:10.070 --> 06:11.470
Why are you cursing at me?

06:12.070 --> 06:12.470
Mr. Li.

06:14.190 --> 06:14.680
Mr. Li.

06:14.800 --> 06:15.730
Noble Consort Yu

06:15.950 --> 06:18.430
understands the greater good and
loves the people like her own children.

06:18.430 --> 06:20.680
How could she do something so despicable?

06:20.680 --> 06:22.340
Don't spread rumors anymore.

06:23.000 --> 06:23.480
Yes.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.810
There must be some misunderstanding.

06:31.940 --> 06:34.400
I must go ask His Majesty
for clarification.

06:35.070 --> 06:37.870
But harem affairs
are His Majesty's family matters.

06:37.870 --> 06:39.930
How can I, a mere subject, interfere?

06:40.040 --> 06:41.950
The Noble Consort once saved my life.

06:41.950 --> 06:43.360
Now that she's in trouble,

06:43.360 --> 06:44.720
how can I just stand by?

06:52.290 --> 06:53.620
But as a court official,

06:53.750 --> 06:55.810
what can I really do for Her Highness?

06:57.390 --> 06:58.800
Li Yunxi, oh Li Yunxi.

06:59.800 --> 07:02.160
So you're such a coward.

07:03.040 --> 07:04.800
She is not only His Majesty's consort

07:04.800 --> 07:06.800
but also his comrade
who fights alongside him.

07:06.800 --> 07:07.950
Are you going to be like those pedantic,

07:07.950 --> 07:09.390
narrow-minded fools

07:09.680 --> 07:11.120
and abandon her after using her

07:11.120 --> 07:12.890
just because she is a woman?

07:17.270 --> 07:18.070
Your Majesty!

07:20.800 --> 07:21.190
I

07:21.680 --> 07:24.340
am willing to counsel
even at the cost of my life!

07:28.560 --> 07:29.290
You're here?

07:31.920 --> 07:32.250
Come.

07:32.640 --> 07:33.930
Please rise.

07:35.830 --> 07:36.630
Don't mind me.

07:36.680 --> 07:37.510
You two talk.

08:07.430 --> 08:08.270
Since everyone is here,

08:08.270 --> 08:08.800
let's...

08:09.160 --> 08:09.630
begin.

08:28.830 --> 08:30.920
The one who killed someone last night
was Li Si.

08:30.920 --> 08:32.470
You're not a wanted criminal.

08:32.470 --> 08:34.000
Why are you being so sneaky?

08:34.510 --> 08:35.309
That's right.

08:38.080 --> 08:38.720
I've been

08:38.909 --> 08:40.440
hiding so carefully all this way.

08:40.440 --> 08:42.169
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

08:47.390 --> 08:48.870
Why did you use internal force
just to throw a bag?

08:48.870 --> 08:49.400
Alright.

08:49.840 --> 08:51.040
Stop fooling around.

08:51.690 --> 08:53.090
To avoid complications,

08:53.630 --> 08:55.840
I have to hastily arrange for you
to leave the city.

08:55.840 --> 08:56.770
Have you decided

08:56.840 --> 08:57.500
where to go?

08:57.790 --> 08:59.840
I'll stay at a farmhouse for a few days

08:59.840 --> 09:01.270
and wait for my companion
before we leave together.

09:01.270 --> 09:02.000
Companion?

09:04.870 --> 09:05.960
You rascal.

09:06.720 --> 09:08.120
You're quite something.

09:08.910 --> 09:10.310
It's only been a few days,

09:10.550 --> 09:13.610
and you've already gained
His Majesty's recognition.

09:14.720 --> 09:15.670
What's his secret order

09:15.670 --> 09:17.200
that you can't even tell me?

09:18.320 --> 09:20.120
You'll have to ask His Majesty.

09:22.390 --> 09:22.990
Forget it.

09:24.390 --> 09:25.240
Now that Dan

09:25.870 --> 09:27.400
is in a dangerous situation

09:27.440 --> 09:29.300
and you're still inexperienced,

09:29.670 --> 09:30.240
you must

09:30.510 --> 09:32.240
be extra careful in everything

09:32.910 --> 09:34.670
and act only after careful planning.

09:34.670 --> 09:36.390
Don't let him down.

09:38.080 --> 09:38.600
Also,

09:39.320 --> 09:40.800
take good care of yourself.

09:40.800 --> 09:42.290
Don't make your master worry.

09:42.290 --> 09:43.020
Don't worry.

09:44.270 --> 09:44.930
Master Bei,

09:45.240 --> 09:46.440
I heard from my master

09:46.720 --> 09:47.960
that you can write poetry.

09:47.960 --> 09:49.360
At this moment of farewell,

09:49.360 --> 09:50.420
how about one poem?

09:53.550 --> 09:54.080
Alright.

10:03.910 --> 10:06.200
The road ahead stretches endlessly,

10:06.790 --> 10:08.840
and the autumn wind is lonely.

10:09.670 --> 10:11.530
If one stands in the wind too long,

10:12.510 --> 10:13.510
one will get cold.

10:17.870 --> 10:19.330
It is indeed getting cold.

10:20.750 --> 10:21.410
Master Bei,

10:22.560 --> 10:23.960
you should head back now.

10:24.120 --> 10:25.250
Until we meet again.

10:25.670 --> 10:26.270
Take care.

10:32.030 --> 10:32.550
Mr. Bei,

10:33.480 --> 10:34.740
if you later discover

10:35.030 --> 10:36.840
that he isn't your old friend's son,

10:36.840 --> 10:40.170
but a lonely soul who came from
another world many years ago,

10:40.270 --> 10:42.270
you'll definitely be heartbroken.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.280
At that time,

10:44.120 --> 10:46.180
will you still treat him the same way?

10:48.510 --> 10:50.360
I have calculated the expected yield

10:50.360 --> 10:52.440
during droughts based on
the crop varieties in each region.

10:52.440 --> 10:53.270
When a drought occurs,

10:53.270 --> 10:55.390
Your Majesty, you can adjust
disaster relief according to

10:55.390 --> 10:56.840
the grain reserves of each province.

10:56.840 --> 10:58.360
Thank you for your hard work, Mr. Cen.

10:58.360 --> 10:59.840
It is my duty.

11:00.720 --> 11:01.510
Your Majesty,

11:01.510 --> 11:02.790
since the reduction of taxes and rents

11:02.790 --> 11:04.200
and the implementation
of the Salt-for-Services Policy,

11:04.200 --> 11:06.080
the people's livelihood
has greatly improved.

11:06.080 --> 11:07.400
-I've visited the villages around...
-Although the Yan people

11:07.400 --> 11:08.720
live in a remote land,

11:09.480 --> 11:12.480
they have always coveted
the prosperity of Great Xia.

11:13.080 --> 11:15.550
I remember in the original story,
once Xiahou Dan died,

11:15.550 --> 11:18.750
The King of Yan immediately took advantage
of the drought to launch an invasion,

11:18.750 --> 11:20.810
clashing fiercely with Prince Duan.

11:22.870 --> 11:24.800
If this diplomatic mission fails,

11:25.320 --> 11:26.720
war will be unavoidable.

11:27.550 --> 11:29.210
It seems we must prepare early

11:29.960 --> 11:31.490
to avoid being defenseless

11:31.670 --> 11:32.840
by the time.

11:32.840 --> 11:35.480
I have visited
over 10 villages near the capital.

11:35.480 --> 11:37.750
And many fields of Yan millet
have been cultivated within the border.

11:37.750 --> 11:39.000
After a few planting seasons,

11:39.000 --> 11:40.960
even without buying seeds from Yan State,

11:40.960 --> 11:43.240
we should be able to handle droughts
in the future.

11:43.240 --> 11:44.280
As General You said

11:44.280 --> 11:46.740
-the day before yesterday...
-General You?

11:48.720 --> 11:49.520
Your Majesty.

11:49.670 --> 11:51.480
Although General You
is the commander of the Right Army,

11:51.480 --> 11:53.320
he has none of the bearing
of a true general.

11:53.320 --> 11:54.670
With him stationed at the southern border,

11:54.670 --> 11:57.000
it will sooner or later become a disaster.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.670
He has good judgment.

11:59.510 --> 12:01.910
This man was a coward
in the original story.

12:02.480 --> 12:05.140
During the Yan-Xia war,
he rushed to surrender.

12:05.200 --> 12:06.910
He truly disgraces his title of general.

12:06.910 --> 12:09.270
I don't expect him
to accomplish anything significant.

12:09.270 --> 12:10.680
But with him in that post,

12:11.270 --> 12:12.400
I can't command him,

12:12.750 --> 12:13.880
nor can Prince Duan.

12:14.600 --> 12:15.870
That's actually not a bad thing.

12:15.870 --> 12:17.120
-But the southern border...
-Mr. Li.

12:17.120 --> 12:18.720
Stop worrying about others.

12:19.270 --> 12:21.240
Tell me about the Ministry of Revenue.

12:21.240 --> 12:22.640
The Ministry of Revenue?

12:25.440 --> 12:26.700
Then there's even more

12:26.910 --> 12:27.790
to report.

12:40.120 --> 12:40.910
What is this?

12:41.360 --> 12:42.620
What nonsense is this?

12:43.200 --> 12:44.730
Take it back and rewrite it!

12:44.870 --> 12:46.070
Here, drink more.

12:46.510 --> 12:47.110
Lord Chen.

12:47.670 --> 12:48.270
Lord Chen.

12:49.150 --> 12:50.420
Can't you see I'm busy?

12:50.510 --> 12:51.550
Take it back and rewrite it.

12:51.550 --> 12:52.150
Lord Chen.

12:52.960 --> 12:53.560
Lord Chen.

12:54.240 --> 12:55.360
This is my corrected version.

12:55.360 --> 12:56.690
Why are you everywhere?

12:56.910 --> 12:57.670
Go away.

12:58.320 --> 12:59.380
In the past 5 years,

12:59.480 --> 13:00.770
the population and common people
of more than 10 counties

13:00.770 --> 13:02.440
have neither increased nor decreased.

13:02.440 --> 13:05.480
Thousands of acres of fertile farmland
have been seized by local gentry,

13:05.480 --> 13:08.480
and not a single person
in the Ministry of Revenue noticed.

13:08.480 --> 13:09.200
After this,

13:09.630 --> 13:10.830
I finally understand

13:10.870 --> 13:12.440
why the records
in each province and county

13:12.440 --> 13:14.900
are full of errors
without anyone noticing,

13:15.320 --> 13:16.610
and why those officials
have been idle for years

13:16.610 --> 13:18.510
without anyone
holding them accountable.

13:18.510 --> 13:19.030
It's simply because

13:19.030 --> 13:21.490
those land-grabbing gentry

13:21.790 --> 13:23.670
are backed by layers of local officials,

13:23.670 --> 13:25.600
and behind those damn officials

13:25.670 --> 13:27.270
are all imperial relatives.

13:27.550 --> 13:28.100
Li!

13:28.480 --> 13:29.630
If we investigate thoroughly,

13:29.630 --> 13:30.480
in the entire Ministry of Revenue,

13:30.480 --> 13:32.740
how many would dare claim they're clean?

13:33.360 --> 13:34.480
If we investigate further,

13:34.480 --> 13:35.630
it leads to the Empress Dowager.

13:35.630 --> 13:37.680
Who can investigate? Who dares to?

13:46.840 --> 13:48.900
If we let them hide their corruption,

13:49.000 --> 13:50.030
when will this land

13:50.030 --> 13:51.760
ever see fairness and justice?

13:51.960 --> 13:53.440
With a vicious woman in power

13:53.440 --> 13:55.040
and no wise ruler to oversee,

13:55.390 --> 13:57.320
no matter how much effort we put in,

13:57.440 --> 13:58.840
it'll be all in vain.

14:09.240 --> 14:09.720
Li.

14:10.480 --> 14:11.910
What you said is true.

14:12.270 --> 14:15.000
But determination alone
cannot change the situation.

14:15.000 --> 14:16.000
If we want to investigate,

14:16.000 --> 14:18.390
we can always use some connections
in the bureaucracy

14:18.390 --> 14:19.720
and find flexible ways.

14:20.030 --> 14:21.890
You want me to exploit loopholes?

14:21.960 --> 14:23.750
Since none of us is willing to stand by,

14:23.750 --> 14:25.080
making some compromises

14:25.080 --> 14:26.120
is acceptable, isn't it?

14:26.120 --> 14:27.440
How should we compromise?

14:27.440 --> 14:29.480
Why don't you demonstrate it yourself,
Lord Er,

14:29.480 --> 14:30.870
and show me?

14:33.120 --> 14:33.850
For example,

14:33.960 --> 14:37.150
we could arrange for some farmers
whose fertile land was seized

14:37.150 --> 14:38.390
to file a petition to His Majesty,

14:38.390 --> 14:41.510
then have a palace servant
subtly report it to the Empress Dowager.

14:41.510 --> 14:43.480
As for the Ministry of Revenue...

14:51.080 --> 14:52.000
Minister,

14:52.320 --> 14:54.650
I heard that after the treasury incident,

14:54.870 --> 14:57.200
the Empress Dowager has been keeping
a close eye on the Ministry of Revenue.

14:57.200 --> 14:58.360
In my humble opinion,

14:58.360 --> 14:59.480
a reform order

14:59.630 --> 15:01.360
will be issued sooner or later.

15:01.510 --> 15:02.320
We might as well

15:02.320 --> 15:05.270
take the initiative and reform
before she orders it.

15:05.960 --> 15:08.340
At least everyone
can save face in the end.

15:08.750 --> 15:11.410
You can rest assured
and leave this matter to me.

15:11.550 --> 15:12.750
What do you think, My Lord?

15:12.750 --> 15:13.610
That's just...

15:13.750 --> 15:15.480
That's the general idea.

15:15.600 --> 15:16.750
Li, you're so eloquent.

15:16.750 --> 15:18.510
Certainly you would put it in a nicer way.

15:18.510 --> 15:19.690
That makes sense.

15:22.670 --> 15:23.470
I believe that

15:23.720 --> 15:24.670
whether a cat is black or white,

15:24.670 --> 15:27.000
as long as it catches mice,
it's a good cat.

15:27.000 --> 15:29.800
Even though our path now
is winding and tortuous,

15:30.510 --> 15:32.440
even the smallest efforts

15:32.510 --> 15:35.640
will eventually pile up
like grains of sand into a tower.

15:35.870 --> 15:37.670
Since Li has finished his report,

15:37.670 --> 15:39.150
let me proceed next.

15:39.200 --> 15:39.720
I haven't fini—

15:39.720 --> 15:41.920
Mr. Er has important matters to report.

15:42.630 --> 15:43.550
Sit down.

15:43.750 --> 15:44.600
What are you doing?

15:44.600 --> 15:45.530
That was enough.

15:45.590 --> 15:48.620
[Kunyu Palace]

16:02.240 --> 16:03.900
Through all these hardships,

16:04.130 --> 16:05.730
thankfully I've had Yong'er

16:06.010 --> 16:07.410
by my side supporting me.

16:09.150 --> 16:09.720
I...

16:10.550 --> 16:11.880
will never let you down.

16:25.910 --> 16:27.510
Xie Yong'er, oh Xie Yong'er.

16:28.290 --> 16:29.200
What are you doing?

16:29.200 --> 16:30.200
Do you want to die?

16:34.720 --> 16:36.960
Your Highness,
why has your period come early?

16:36.960 --> 16:38.240
It's not time yet.

16:38.260 --> 16:38.600
I...

16:43.870 --> 16:44.630
Well...

16:48.240 --> 16:49.370
It's not the period.

16:50.510 --> 16:51.320
Perhaps...

16:51.750 --> 16:52.440
I bumped...

16:52.910 --> 16:54.240
into something somewhere.

16:54.240 --> 16:55.400
Are you injured?

16:55.630 --> 16:57.670
If you're injured, why didn't you tell me?

16:57.670 --> 16:58.960
I'll go get Physician Xiao.

16:58.960 --> 16:59.490
I'm fine.

17:00.270 --> 17:01.370
How can you be fine?

17:01.440 --> 17:02.720
If you're injured, you can't attend

17:02.720 --> 17:03.670
to His Majesty in the bedchamber.

17:03.670 --> 17:04.790
We need to report this
to the Service Room.

17:04.790 --> 17:06.170
I said I'm fine.

17:12.349 --> 17:13.950
I was so careless that night.

17:14.510 --> 17:15.650
After all these nights of service,

17:15.650 --> 17:17.650
His Majesty hasn't even touched me.

17:18.250 --> 17:19.640
If I'm pregnant with Prince Duan's child,

17:19.640 --> 17:21.920
the consequences would be unimaginable.

17:21.920 --> 17:23.319
I need to think of an idea.

17:27.240 --> 17:29.840
Go prepare
two bright-colored outfits for me.

17:30.160 --> 17:30.750
Tonight,

17:32.750 --> 17:34.080
I'll go see His Majesty.

17:36.920 --> 17:37.720
This way,

17:37.880 --> 17:38.950
merchants will compete to transport grain

17:38.950 --> 17:40.030
in exchange for
Salt Transportation and Sales License.

17:40.030 --> 17:41.510
The profits from salt trade are enormous.

17:41.510 --> 17:43.640
Merchants will naturally flock to it.

17:43.680 --> 17:44.480
In the future,

17:44.640 --> 17:46.200
the fight to control the monopoly

17:46.200 --> 17:50.660
will lead to collusion between officials
and merchants, breeding corruption.

17:51.590 --> 17:53.400
But wasn't the Salt-for-Services Policy

17:53.400 --> 17:54.680
your proposal?

17:58.790 --> 17:59.590
Your Majesty,

17:59.720 --> 18:01.880
every dynasty's policies have their flaws.

18:01.880 --> 18:05.070
Today, the Salt-for-Services Policy
does benefit the people.

18:05.070 --> 18:06.510
When its drawbacks become apparent,

18:06.510 --> 18:08.770
it should be replaced with new policies.

18:10.920 --> 18:11.680
By then,

18:12.350 --> 18:12.980
Er,

18:13.310 --> 18:15.840
you will already hold high office,
won't you?

18:17.000 --> 18:17.310
No.

18:18.440 --> 18:19.350
By that time,

18:21.110 --> 18:22.770
I should no longer be in court.

18:29.400 --> 18:31.680
Those who hold high office

18:31.720 --> 18:33.200
should be people like you.

18:33.720 --> 18:34.750
The court by then

18:34.790 --> 18:36.750
will surely allow talents like you

18:36.770 --> 18:37.830
to achieve great things

18:37.830 --> 18:39.490
and realize their ambitions.

18:40.030 --> 18:40.640
Mr. Li,

18:41.270 --> 18:42.440
I have never forgotten

18:42.440 --> 18:44.350
what we said that day
on the pleasure boat.

18:44.350 --> 18:46.410
What we seek is not power or scheming,

18:46.680 --> 18:49.140
but the wealth and well-being
of the people.

18:49.310 --> 18:51.240
Otherwise, how are we different

18:51.240 --> 18:52.550
from Prince Duan's sycophants?

18:52.550 --> 18:54.270
How could we face Du

18:54.640 --> 18:56.440
and fulfill our promises to him?

18:57.240 --> 18:58.960
We must carry his sincerity

18:59.590 --> 19:01.480
and spare no effort to support Great Xia.

19:01.480 --> 19:03.010
We will do everything we can

19:04.000 --> 19:05.270
to support our wise ruler.

19:05.270 --> 19:07.270
The corrupt officials will pay the price.

19:07.270 --> 19:07.930
We will soon

19:09.270 --> 19:10.730
restore your reputation.

19:13.400 --> 19:14.310
Mr. Er is right.

19:15.350 --> 19:17.640
Those who accomplish great things
do not get caught up in trivial matters.

19:17.640 --> 19:18.840
His Majesty once said

19:18.920 --> 19:19.930
we are one team,

19:20.200 --> 19:22.030
each with strengths and weaknesses,

19:22.030 --> 19:23.490
and should work together.

19:25.880 --> 19:26.590
Chen Danian

19:27.720 --> 19:29.380
only cares for wine and women.

19:29.440 --> 19:31.640
Mr. Li, you don't like dealing with him.

19:32.350 --> 19:33.680
I'll take on the burden.

19:33.920 --> 19:34.720
Leave it to me.

19:37.880 --> 19:39.270
The Ministry of Works
has many tedious matters.

19:39.270 --> 19:40.640
I am good with calculations.

19:40.640 --> 19:42.070
Mr. Yang, if you need me,

19:42.590 --> 19:43.240
just ask.

19:47.130 --> 19:48.560
I only know farming.

19:48.960 --> 19:49.690
My health...

19:50.860 --> 19:52.660
I might not be of much help to you.

19:53.790 --> 19:54.520
I'm ashamed.

19:56.160 --> 19:56.820
So ashamed.

20:06.310 --> 20:06.750
Cen,

20:07.240 --> 20:08.240
you like farming.

20:08.550 --> 20:09.750
If your ox gets tired,

20:09.960 --> 20:10.620
I'm strong.

20:11.030 --> 20:12.160
I can take its place.

20:22.110 --> 20:24.040
Prince Duan has an army of 100,000.

20:24.270 --> 20:26.400
The Empress Dowager has the entire court.

20:26.400 --> 20:26.930
And we...

20:28.960 --> 20:30.160
only have each other.

20:35.840 --> 20:37.640
I'm not particularly talented,

20:38.330 --> 20:40.840
but being able
to meet all of you in this lifetime

20:40.840 --> 20:42.440
is reason enough for a toast.

20:48.070 --> 20:49.600
I'll use tea in place of wine

20:49.750 --> 20:50.880
and toast to you all.

20:50.970 --> 20:51.640
Your Highness.

20:51.640 --> 20:52.500
Your Highness.

20:54.110 --> 20:55.770
The world is like a long night.

20:56.480 --> 20:58.810
Who could change it with a single cry?

21:00.040 --> 21:01.770
But to struggle alongside you,

21:02.750 --> 21:04.080
even if we fall halfway,

21:10.870 --> 21:12.000
I know I'm not alone.

21:22.400 --> 21:22.960
Li Yunxi.

21:27.590 --> 21:28.390
Your Majesty.

21:28.480 --> 21:30.140
Keep organizing the records.

21:30.480 --> 21:31.540
Don't tell anyone.

21:32.240 --> 21:33.640
Give them directly to me.

21:34.070 --> 21:35.600
They'll be useful someday.

21:41.070 --> 21:42.470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

21:42.550 --> 21:42.880
Rise.

21:52.550 --> 21:54.550
It's because people like them exist

21:55.110 --> 21:57.770
that it makes me feel
leaving everything behind

21:58.030 --> 21:59.230
would be despicable.

22:02.720 --> 22:03.310
Then I...

22:04.640 --> 22:06.900
should properly thank these ministers.

22:08.350 --> 22:10.080
They make me know I'm not alone.

22:12.960 --> 22:14.020
Stop imitating me.

22:15.510 --> 22:17.840
It's getting late. I should head back now.

22:19.870 --> 22:21.530
Why not stay for dinner first?

22:21.750 --> 22:22.240
Hot pot.

22:22.550 --> 22:23.350
Your Majesty!

22:23.920 --> 22:24.720
Your Majesty!

22:25.240 --> 22:26.040
Your Majesty.

22:27.000 --> 22:27.800
Your Majesty,

22:28.030 --> 22:29.430
Consort Xie requests...

22:31.480 --> 22:32.210
an audience.

22:34.160 --> 22:35.490
I will take my leave now.

22:42.160 --> 22:43.000
Consort Xie?

22:44.070 --> 22:44.530
Well...

22:44.920 --> 22:46.000
the hot pot...

22:46.000 --> 22:47.860
The secret passage is over there.

22:48.840 --> 22:51.570
Solidifying your image
of favoring Consort Xie?

22:52.270 --> 22:52.720
I think

22:53.310 --> 22:54.880
you're just getting back at me

22:54.880 --> 22:57.740
for making Xie Yong'er serve you
in the bedchamber.

23:05.920 --> 23:06.900
Just admit it.

23:07.610 --> 23:09.940
Seeing a bunch of women fighting over you,

23:10.680 --> 23:13.010
you're secretly enjoying it, aren't you?

23:14.930 --> 23:17.270
And now you're turning your head away?
What's that supposed to mean?

23:17.270 --> 23:19.160
I know men too well.

23:19.680 --> 23:21.140
You say no with your mouth,

23:21.400 --> 23:23.600
but inside you're probably delighted.

23:26.830 --> 23:27.680
However,

23:28.350 --> 23:30.810
we just tricked Prince Duan
at Banyue House.

23:31.110 --> 23:33.110
And Xie Yong'er came at this time...

23:33.920 --> 23:36.050
Could she be snooping for Prince Duan?

23:37.270 --> 23:38.530
I can't let her do that.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.690
I'd better stay and keep watch.

23:41.200 --> 23:42.200
You're so stupid.

23:42.510 --> 23:44.570
What if Xie Yong'er manipulates you?

23:46.550 --> 23:47.720
It makes perfect sense.

23:47.720 --> 23:49.120
Completely reasonable.

24:02.350 --> 24:03.810
Greetings, Your Majesty.

24:04.720 --> 24:05.920
My dear, you're here.

24:06.350 --> 24:07.880
I have prepared wine for...

24:14.000 --> 24:14.440
I...

24:15.070 --> 24:15.880
have prepared the wine.

24:15.880 --> 24:17.830
Your Majesty,
please don't trouble yourself.

24:17.830 --> 24:19.490
I've already had some drinks.

24:21.510 --> 24:23.550
Is she imitating me?

24:25.590 --> 24:27.120
Wine is the essence of food.

24:27.160 --> 24:29.420
The more you drink, the younger you feel.

24:29.790 --> 24:31.320
Let's play a drinking game.

24:32.750 --> 24:34.750
I don't want to play drinking games.

24:35.590 --> 24:37.050
Then what do you want to do?

24:40.830 --> 24:43.500
I want you to guess

24:44.510 --> 24:45.690
what I have...

24:46.920 --> 24:48.160
in my sleeve.

25:01.000 --> 25:01.720
Flowers.

25:04.680 --> 25:06.810
Xie Yong'er really knows how to flirt.

25:07.270 --> 25:08.750
Can CEO Dan handle this?

25:09.160 --> 25:09.820
Flowers...

25:15.190 --> 25:15.990
Your Majesty.

25:16.200 --> 25:18.070
Your Majesty, would you like to see

25:18.070 --> 25:19.750
what I have...

25:21.160 --> 25:22.420
underneath this robe?

25:23.750 --> 25:24.810
My dear, calm down.

25:27.720 --> 25:29.440
How did it fall down?

25:30.940 --> 25:33.070
She's much more flirtatious than I am.

25:33.110 --> 25:34.640
You don't like this either?

25:35.550 --> 25:36.640
Then I guess

25:37.030 --> 25:38.750
you must want to know

25:39.350 --> 25:40.960
what's underneath...

25:42.790 --> 25:44.240
my skirt.

25:49.160 --> 25:51.290
Xie Yong'er, you're quite something!

25:51.760 --> 25:53.030
My dear, don't come any closer.

25:53.030 --> 25:54.030
You must be drunk.

25:54.200 --> 25:56.260
You can pretend I'm drunk if you want.

25:59.640 --> 26:00.400
Your Majesty!

26:00.400 --> 26:03.060
-Don't move!
-Your Majesty, what are you doing?

26:03.160 --> 26:03.590
Your Majesty!

26:03.590 --> 26:04.350
What's happening?

26:04.350 --> 26:07.010
-It hurts, Your Majesty!
-I can't see anything!

26:07.270 --> 26:08.400
Your Majesty, be gentle.

26:08.400 --> 26:09.140
It hurts!

26:10.790 --> 26:13.030
Your Majesty,
do you truly feel nothing for me?

26:13.030 --> 26:13.510
Yes.

26:14.400 --> 26:14.880
An Xian!

26:18.960 --> 26:19.490
I'm here.

26:20.550 --> 26:21.750
Consort Xie is drunk.

26:21.960 --> 26:23.490
Send her back to her palace.

26:23.510 --> 26:23.800
Yes.

26:25.400 --> 26:25.860
Guards!

26:31.690 --> 26:32.550
Carry her away.

26:34.590 --> 26:37.520
What's wrong with that silly girl
Xie Yong'er today?

26:37.680 --> 26:39.960
-Doesn't she only care about Prince Duan?
-Your Majesty!

26:39.960 --> 26:40.590
-Is it Prince Duan
-Your Majesty!

26:40.590 --> 26:42.120
who made her put on this act?

26:42.350 --> 26:44.510
Or did Prince Duan
break Xie Yong'er's heart

26:44.510 --> 26:46.840
and she switched her target to Xiahou Dan?

26:47.110 --> 26:48.380
What does she want?

27:01.400 --> 27:02.440
You...

27:04.480 --> 27:05.030
I...

27:08.680 --> 27:10.010
What are you doing here?

27:12.350 --> 27:13.310
I, uh...

27:15.400 --> 27:15.790
I...

27:16.350 --> 27:17.010
I got stuck.

27:22.510 --> 27:23.310
You got stuck?

27:25.920 --> 27:27.580
I've been eating well lately.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.570
I've gained weight.

27:40.240 --> 27:41.030
Yu Wanyin,

27:41.030 --> 27:43.000
what have you become?

27:43.000 --> 27:43.950
You...

27:44.440 --> 27:46.030
You were eavesdropping!

27:46.270 --> 27:48.350
You're like those jealous,

27:48.350 --> 27:50.750
brainless cannon fodder in novels!

27:50.960 --> 27:52.270
How embarrassing!

27:56.920 --> 27:58.240
Why don't you come out first?

27:58.240 --> 27:58.900
She's gone.

28:00.070 --> 28:00.830
Forget it.

28:01.240 --> 28:02.640
There are too many people around.

28:02.640 --> 28:04.200
It wouldn't look good
if someone sees me here.

28:04.200 --> 28:05.000
I'd better go.

28:05.240 --> 28:06.440
I won't let anyone in.

28:09.310 --> 28:10.240
Forget it.

28:10.830 --> 28:13.070
Eunuch An just caught us.

28:14.070 --> 28:14.800
I'm leaving.

28:31.920 --> 28:33.180
Xie Yong'er just left,

28:33.920 --> 28:36.120
and Xiahou Dan came to check the tunnel.

28:36.480 --> 28:38.080
How did he know I hadn't left?

28:39.590 --> 28:40.920
I didn't make any sound.

28:43.110 --> 28:43.920
Unless...

28:46.240 --> 28:48.000
Unless he wanted to find me.

28:50.790 --> 28:51.720
He didn't expect

28:52.310 --> 28:54.170
that I witnessed the whole thing.

28:54.670 --> 28:56.000
And he was embarrassed.

28:59.190 --> 29:01.300
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

29:01.540 --> 29:02.850
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

29:03.130 --> 29:05.330
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

29:05.650 --> 29:07.080
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

29:07.120 --> 29:09.510
♪ Words unspoken ♪

29:11.040 --> 29:13.500
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

29:15.160 --> 29:17.340
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

29:17.640 --> 29:18.680
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

29:19.180 --> 29:21.190
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

29:21.660 --> 29:23.020
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

29:23.120 --> 29:25.570
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

29:25.550 --> 29:26.390
Yu Wanyin.

29:27.120 --> 29:30.460
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

29:27.510 --> 29:29.910
Have you been living so comfortably lately

29:30.270 --> 29:32.000
that you actually have time
to think about such nonsense?

29:31.040 --> 29:34.470
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

29:33.440 --> 29:35.240
What's more important,
love or staying alive?

29:35.140 --> 29:38.130
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

29:35.510 --> 29:36.720
Staying alive, of course.

29:36.720 --> 29:38.570
That's the most important thing.

29:38.570 --> 29:40.470
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

29:40.700 --> 29:42.380
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

29:42.640 --> 29:44.300
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

29:44.650 --> 29:46.310
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

29:47.170 --> 29:50.280
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

29:47.880 --> 29:49.030
But tonight's moon

29:50.070 --> 29:51.000
is so beautiful.

29:51.120 --> 29:53.530
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

29:53.600 --> 29:54.710
♪ Still unchanged ♪

29:55.210 --> 29:58.070
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

29:58.670 --> 30:00.120
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

30:00.230 --> 30:07.430
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

30:20.590 --> 30:21.790
Move these out first.

30:25.110 --> 30:25.440
Here.

30:34.720 --> 30:35.400
Your Highness.

30:35.400 --> 30:36.130
Please rise.

30:36.640 --> 30:37.550
The weather's getting cold.

30:37.550 --> 30:38.830
I made some ginger soup for everyone.

30:38.830 --> 30:39.680
Drink it while it's hot.

30:39.680 --> 30:40.550
Thank you, Your Highness.

30:40.550 --> 30:42.010
Thank you, Your Highness.

30:42.510 --> 30:42.840
Here.

30:44.440 --> 30:46.770
There's no rush with this secret passage.

30:47.550 --> 30:48.480
His Majesty said

30:48.790 --> 30:50.400
this secret passage is used every day.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.720
We must hurry to widen it.

30:51.720 --> 30:53.350
We can't let Your Highness suffer.

30:53.350 --> 30:53.880
Every...

30:54.000 --> 30:55.030
every day?

30:55.400 --> 30:57.240
CEO Dan is embarrassing me.

30:58.680 --> 31:00.400
Why hasn't His Majesty
dismissed the court yet today?

31:00.400 --> 31:01.260
Your Highness,

31:01.440 --> 31:02.510
I heard they're still arguing over

31:02.510 --> 31:04.920
whether to let the Yan envoys
enter the city.

31:04.920 --> 31:06.200
His Majesty just left court

31:06.200 --> 31:08.240
and got trapped in the Imperial Study.

31:08.240 --> 31:09.040
Your Majesty,

31:09.110 --> 31:10.720
the Yan people
claim to be celebrating your birthday,

31:10.720 --> 31:12.040
but everyone knows

31:12.240 --> 31:14.200
what they really want to do.

31:14.720 --> 31:15.550
Yes.

31:15.550 --> 31:18.000
If we open the city gates
and welcome them in,

31:18.000 --> 31:20.240
wouldn't that be like
inviting a wolf into the house,

31:20.240 --> 31:22.170
leading to endless consequences?

31:22.640 --> 31:23.310
Yes.

31:23.310 --> 31:24.110
That's right.

31:24.720 --> 31:26.120
Minister, how do you know

31:27.110 --> 31:28.640
that the Yan people's visit

31:28.960 --> 31:30.090
is ill-intentioned

31:31.000 --> 31:33.460
rather than genuinely seeking peace talks?

31:34.160 --> 31:34.920
Peace talks?

31:35.440 --> 31:36.240
Your Majesty,

31:36.350 --> 31:37.600
we've been fighting for over ten years.

31:37.600 --> 31:39.070
If they wanted to talk,
they would've done it earlier.

31:39.070 --> 31:40.750
Why would they wait until today?

31:40.750 --> 31:41.280
Exactly.

31:42.000 --> 31:44.550
We have 100,000 troops
bravely fighting them at the border,

31:44.550 --> 31:47.440
yet the court wants to
welcome them as honored guests.

31:47.440 --> 31:49.240
Your Majesty, if you insist on this,

31:49.240 --> 31:51.880
it'll disappoint our soldiers
at the border.

31:52.310 --> 31:53.310
Yes, Your Majesty.

31:53.310 --> 31:55.510
This must be a conspiracy
by the Yan people.

31:55.510 --> 31:56.920
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.720
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

31:58.720 --> 32:00.450
If we can truly hold peace talks

32:00.640 --> 32:02.240
and end the war at the border,

32:02.510 --> 32:03.840
these 100,000 soldiers

32:04.680 --> 32:06.480
can reunite with their families

32:06.830 --> 32:07.830
and enjoy peace.

32:09.550 --> 32:10.950
Won't that be a blessing?

32:11.070 --> 32:12.510
Your Majesty, you make it sound simple.

32:12.510 --> 32:13.400
Over the past 10 years,

32:13.400 --> 32:15.480
we've paid such a heavy price.

32:15.590 --> 32:16.790
Now that we have the upper hand,

32:16.790 --> 32:18.070
we should press the advantage

32:18.070 --> 32:19.730
and wipe out the Yan people.

32:19.960 --> 32:21.880
Yet now you want to give up halfway.

32:21.880 --> 32:22.760
How are we

32:22.880 --> 32:25.210
supposed to explain this to the soldiers?

32:25.480 --> 32:27.590
Yes, Mr. Cao is right.

32:27.640 --> 32:28.480
How can we explain to them?

32:28.480 --> 32:29.090
Exactly.

32:29.350 --> 32:30.790
Please calm down.

32:31.200 --> 32:32.590
What we're discussing now is

32:32.590 --> 32:35.160
whether to let them enter the city
to celebrate my birthday.

32:35.160 --> 32:36.830
We're not talking about peace talks yet.

32:36.830 --> 32:37.360
Besides,

32:37.680 --> 32:39.410
I observed the stars last night

32:39.790 --> 32:41.940
and saw Saturn aligning with Jupiter.

32:42.160 --> 32:43.270
This foretells...

32:43.270 --> 32:46.070
You Imperial Astronomers
always go with the wind.

32:46.200 --> 32:47.240
If solving problems could really be done

32:47.240 --> 32:48.960
with just a few divinations like you do,

32:48.960 --> 32:50.510
what would we ministers be for?

32:50.510 --> 32:51.960
Exactly!

32:52.590 --> 32:56.590
-Please reconsider, Your Majesty!
-Please reconsider, Your Majesty!

33:32.200 --> 33:34.750
We cannot invite the wolf into the house,
Your Majesty!

33:34.750 --> 33:36.680
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!
-Yes, Your Majesty.

33:36.680 --> 33:38.720
We can't let the Yan people
get into Great Xia!

33:38.720 --> 33:40.240
Your Majesty, please reconsider!

33:40.240 --> 33:41.880
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!
-Your Majesty.

33:41.880 --> 33:44.240
We cannot invite the wolf into the house,
Your Majesty!

33:44.240 --> 33:45.040
Your Majesty!

33:45.590 --> 33:46.390
Your Majesty!

33:47.110 --> 33:48.590
-We can't do that!
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!

33:48.590 --> 33:50.030
Your Majesty, please reconsider!

33:50.030 --> 33:50.830
Your Majesty!

33:50.960 --> 33:52.830
We can't do that! We can!

33:52.830 --> 33:53.200
Your Majesty!

33:53.200 --> 33:54.720
We can't do that!

33:54.720 --> 33:56.350
Please reconsider, Your Majesty!

33:56.350 --> 33:57.150
Your Majesty!

33:57.830 --> 33:58.590
Your Majesty!

33:58.590 --> 33:59.270
Your Majesty!

33:59.270 --> 34:00.300
Your Majesty!

34:11.760 --> 34:12.760
This Xiahou Dan.

34:13.550 --> 34:14.760
It's almost dark.

34:15.000 --> 34:16.460
Why hasn't he arrived yet?

34:17.000 --> 34:18.659
I've been waiting for so long.

34:22.280 --> 34:24.280
He can't possibly be skipping dinner,
can he?

34:24.280 --> 34:25.080
That won't do.

34:39.760 --> 34:41.760
It's indeed much more spacious now.

34:43.250 --> 34:44.570
This Xiahou Dan.

34:45.400 --> 34:46.920
If you're skipping dinner,

34:46.920 --> 34:49.520
you should at least send someone
to let me know.

34:50.070 --> 34:51.199
Just how busy are you

34:51.960 --> 34:54.630
that you can't even spare the time
to send a message?

34:54.630 --> 34:56.630
This Xiahou Dan is driving me crazy!

35:02.710 --> 35:04.840
Yu Wanyin, what are you doing?

35:05.840 --> 35:07.480
You're now a demonic consort
who brings disaster to the country.

35:07.480 --> 35:09.000
You used to be
a heartless corporate slave.

35:09.000 --> 35:09.860
Look at you now.

35:11.320 --> 35:13.070
You're not focusing on your career,

35:13.070 --> 35:15.000
and you're even chasing after him.

35:15.440 --> 35:15.960
Go back.

35:21.000 --> 35:21.670
So what?

35:22.150 --> 35:23.590
If he truly has something urgent,

35:23.590 --> 35:24.450
isn't it normal

35:25.070 --> 35:26.110
for me to go ask?

35:26.800 --> 35:27.440
Besides,

35:28.280 --> 35:29.440
isn't this secret passage

35:29.440 --> 35:30.630
meant to be used?

35:35.320 --> 35:36.050
He's coming.

35:37.670 --> 35:38.130
Wanyin.

35:38.670 --> 35:39.840
I was just looking for you.

35:39.840 --> 35:40.500
Dan is sick.

35:40.670 --> 35:41.000
Come.

35:48.450 --> 35:50.240
Zhang San's Diary.

35:50.260 --> 35:51.710
When three people are together,

35:51.710 --> 35:54.570
there's always something
to learn from each other.

35:54.800 --> 35:55.970
I will select

35:55.970 --> 35:57.510
-their good qualities and follow them,
-The Empress Dowager is gone.

35:57.510 --> 35:59.630
-The Emperor doesn't care about me.
-their bad qualities

35:59.630 --> 36:01.800
-and avoid them.
-The new Empress is not a good person.

36:01.800 --> 36:02.620
-Her eyes...
-Confucius said,

36:02.620 --> 36:03.440
while standing by a river...

36:03.440 --> 36:05.840
Every time our eyes meet,
I get goosebumps.

36:06.030 --> 36:08.390
Greetings, Your Majesty.

36:17.590 --> 36:18.070
Mother.

36:21.190 --> 36:22.530
You're studying?

36:23.440 --> 36:24.630
Your Majesty,

36:25.230 --> 36:28.320
the Crown Prince has been studying
the Analects of Confucius lately.

36:28.320 --> 36:29.390
I thought

36:29.630 --> 36:31.620
that as a Confucian classic,

36:32.030 --> 36:35.000
it can teach him how to
cultivate himself and govern the state,

36:35.000 --> 36:36.070
so that in the future

36:36.070 --> 36:38.930
he can shoulder the responsibilities
of the realm.

36:39.590 --> 36:40.920
The Analects of Confucius

36:40.920 --> 36:42.230
is profound.

36:43.320 --> 36:45.380
The Crown Prince is still very young.

36:45.800 --> 36:47.660
Might it be too difficult for him?

36:47.960 --> 36:49.290
I believe

36:49.510 --> 36:51.550
he should proceed step by step.

36:53.190 --> 36:55.630
What about the Thousand Character Classic?

36:55.630 --> 36:58.440
It is full of principles
on conduct and behavior,

36:59.630 --> 37:01.030
and would be easier

37:01.800 --> 37:03.460
for the Crown Prince to learn.

37:07.440 --> 37:09.590
Study the Thousand Character Classic?

37:09.590 --> 37:11.230
She's afraid I'll learn too much

37:11.230 --> 37:12.690
and become capable enough

37:12.760 --> 37:14.070
that she can no longer control me.

37:14.070 --> 37:15.110
Does she want to raise me
into a useless puppet

37:15.110 --> 37:16.640
she can manipulate at will?

37:17.280 --> 37:17.680
No way.

37:18.190 --> 37:20.320
I can't just sit here waiting for doom.

37:22.190 --> 37:22.760
Dan,

37:24.030 --> 37:25.190
what do you think?

37:27.230 --> 37:27.760
Mother,

37:28.710 --> 37:31.090
the Imperial Study is so quiet and lonely.

37:31.480 --> 37:33.480
I'm here alone every day,

37:33.960 --> 37:35.690
and it's truly lonely and dull.

37:36.760 --> 37:38.090
I beg for your kindness.

37:39.630 --> 37:40.950
Even one companion

37:41.150 --> 37:41.960
would be nice.

37:43.230 --> 37:44.100
Your Highness,

37:44.480 --> 37:46.190
Her Majesty has instructed that

37:46.190 --> 37:46.850
from now on,

37:47.230 --> 37:48.440
the Second Prince

37:48.840 --> 37:50.190
will study with you.

37:50.330 --> 37:53.020
[Young Xiahou Bo]

37:50.710 --> 37:52.400
Greetings, Your Highness.

37:53.670 --> 37:54.200
Brother,

37:54.550 --> 37:55.950
no need for formalities.

37:58.280 --> 38:00.540
I was just worried about having no one...

38:01.800 --> 38:03.700
I will be a good study companion

38:03.880 --> 38:05.810
and not disappoint your kindness.

38:07.110 --> 38:09.070
He doesn't seem to like me much.

38:10.110 --> 38:11.110
It doesn't matter.

38:11.110 --> 38:12.230
After spending time together,

38:12.230 --> 38:13.890
we'll surely become friends.

38:14.990 --> 38:18.270
[Thousand Character Classic]

38:15.110 --> 38:16.970
Dark is the sky, yellow the earth.

38:17.280 --> 38:19.080
The universe was vast and crude.

38:19.760 --> 38:21.760
The sun goes down, the moon comes up.

38:21.890 --> 38:23.550
The stars spread as dots.

38:24.480 --> 38:26.100
Winter succeeds summer.

38:26.670 --> 38:28.930
Autumn harvest follows winter storage.

38:29.320 --> 38:31.180
The surplus days make a leap year.

38:31.510 --> 38:33.290
Music pipes regulate the sun.

38:51.320 --> 38:52.190
Your Highness,

38:52.880 --> 38:53.970
pay attention.

38:55.230 --> 38:55.750
Master,

38:56.070 --> 38:57.400
I was the one dozing off.

38:57.510 --> 38:58.800
You punished the wrong person.

38:58.800 --> 39:00.800
The Crown Prince has a noble status.

39:01.190 --> 39:02.280
Even if he makes mistakes,

39:02.280 --> 39:03.440
the punishment should be taken by

39:03.440 --> 39:04.800
his study companion.

39:09.150 --> 39:09.610
Master,

39:10.400 --> 39:11.480
how can you do this?

39:12.000 --> 39:13.420
I was the one who made the mistake.

39:13.420 --> 39:15.350
I should be the one being punished.

39:15.550 --> 39:16.410
The other one.

39:30.360 --> 39:32.800
How is it that
after getting a study companion,

39:32.800 --> 39:34.300
your studies

39:34.710 --> 39:36.250
have become even worse?

39:37.360 --> 39:38.600
Why is that?

39:41.190 --> 39:41.650
Mother,

39:42.550 --> 39:43.430
I am foolish

39:43.920 --> 39:45.520
and always anger the Master.

39:46.590 --> 39:48.110
I even caused trouble for my brother

39:48.110 --> 39:50.240
that he couldn't focus on his lessons.

39:50.360 --> 39:50.900
Perhaps

39:51.230 --> 39:52.280
the Master

39:53.280 --> 39:55.010
should tutor me alone instead.

39:55.590 --> 39:56.920
Crown Prince,

39:57.320 --> 39:59.980
you're the Crown Prince.
How could you be wrong?

40:00.800 --> 40:01.930
The study companion

40:01.990 --> 40:03.630
is here to assist you.

40:04.550 --> 40:05.830
If he's not attentive,

40:06.510 --> 40:07.590
that's his fault.

40:10.960 --> 40:12.760
I failed
to properly support the Crown Prince

40:12.760 --> 40:14.190
and disrupted his studies.

40:14.190 --> 40:15.990
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

40:17.760 --> 40:20.320
Who gave you permission
to speak in front of me?

40:20.320 --> 40:21.980
Your mother, that lowly maid,

40:22.190 --> 40:24.630
talked out of turn while serving

40:24.630 --> 40:25.800
the Crown Prince's birth mother

40:25.800 --> 40:27.710
and was slapped to death.

40:28.230 --> 40:30.690
Are you planning
to follow in her footsteps?

40:32.550 --> 40:33.210
I was wrong.

40:33.760 --> 40:35.280
I will be careful with my words
and actions from now on

40:35.280 --> 40:37.880
and serve the Crown Prince
with full devotion.

40:42.550 --> 40:43.350
Crown Prince.

40:47.440 --> 40:49.170
Don't be afraid, Crown Prince.

40:49.630 --> 40:51.030
There's no need to worry.

40:52.110 --> 40:54.800
Your father has many sons.

40:55.510 --> 40:57.040
If he doesn't perform well,

40:57.440 --> 41:00.040
I can simply find you
another study companion.

41:07.910 --> 41:11.070
[Thousand Character Classic]

41:30.630 --> 41:32.360
All of you, hold out your hands.

41:39.330 --> 41:39.790
Master,

41:40.400 --> 41:41.530
I wasn't dozing off.

41:42.000 --> 41:43.530
Why are you punishing them?

41:44.030 --> 41:46.000
Her Majesty specifically instructed

41:46.000 --> 41:47.800
that when the Crown Prince's headaches
act up,

41:47.800 --> 41:50.030
someone beside him
must feel even more pain

41:50.030 --> 41:50.880
to relieve it.

41:51.320 --> 41:52.560
Master! Master!

41:52.710 --> 41:53.510
I'm not in pain!

41:53.510 --> 41:54.590
I forbid you to hit them!

41:54.590 --> 41:55.370
Crown Prince, why are you

41:55.370 --> 41:56.320
-pretending to be kind?
-Master!

41:56.320 --> 41:57.630
With Her Majesty caring about you,

41:57.630 --> 41:59.480
you should take better care
of your precious self.

41:59.480 --> 42:00.210
Master!

42:02.360 --> 42:03.710
We dare not let you plead for us.

42:03.710 --> 42:08.040
I'll take a few hits and consider it
dispelling misfortune for Your Highness.

42:08.320 --> 42:09.400
Master! Master!

42:09.480 --> 42:10.080
No crying!

42:10.280 --> 42:11.190
Hold out your hand!

42:11.190 --> 42:11.710
Master!

42:13.070 --> 42:14.730
Sixth Brother is still young.

42:15.000 --> 42:15.850
I'll take the punishment in his place!
